              </svg>
              <p class="text-brand-gray text-sm">Free tournament entry</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p class="text-brand-gray text-sm text-center mt-8">
      <a href="/contact" class="text-brand-orange hover:brightness-110 no-underline font-semibold">Visit us in person to sign up</a> • No long-term commitment • Cancel anytime • Walk-in rates also available
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
